      "body": "另外，我个人觉得更理想的解决方案，建议是这样，仅供参考：\n\n``` html\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <div onclick=\"{{itemClick($index)}}\" class=\"OilItem OilItem_{{IsDefault}}\" repeat=\"{{OilItems}}\" >\n      <text class=\"f28 OilItem-tx OilItem-tx-{{IsDefault}}\">{{OilName}}</text>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<style>\n  .OilItem{\n      flex:1;\n      width: 135px;\n      height: 76px;\n      border-width:  1px;\n      border-color: #ff7519;\n      border-radius: 10px;\n      text-align: center;\n      position: relative;\n      font-size: 28px;\n      margin-left: 10px;\n   }\n   .OilItem_false {\n     background-color: #ffffff;\n   }\n   .OilItem_true{\n    background-color: #ff7519\n   }\n   .OilItem-tx{\n      text-align: center;\n      padding-top: 18px;\n   }\n   .OilItem-tx-false{\n      color: #ff7519;\n   }\n   .OilItem-tx-true{\n      color: #fff\n   }\n</style>\n\n<script>\nmodule.exports = {\n  methods: {\n    itemClick: function(index, e) {\n      for (var i = 0; i < this.OilItems.length; i++) {\n        if (i === index) {\n          this.OilItems[i].IsDefault = true;\n        } else {\n          this.OilItems[i].IsDefault = false;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<script type=\"data\">\n{OilItems:[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"OilName\": \"100元\",\n    \"OilCode\": \"OilItem_10001\",\n    \"Discount\": \"9.95折\",\n    \"IsDefault\": \"false\",\n    \"ItemPrice\": 99.5\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"OilName\": \"200元\",\n    \"OilCode\": \"OilItem_88888\",\n    \"Discount\": \"9.95折\",\n    \"IsDefault\": \"false\",\n    \"ItemPrice\": 199\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 3,\n    \"OilName\": \"500元\",\n    \"OilCode\": \"OilItem_10003\",\n    \"Discount\": \"9.95折\",\n    \"IsDefault\": \"true\",\n    \"ItemPrice\": 497.5\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 4,\n    \"OilName\": \"1000元\",\n    \"OilCode\": \"OilItem_10004\",\n    \"Discount\": \"9.95折\",\n    \"IsDefault\": \"false\",\n    \"ItemPrice\": 995\n  }\n]}\n</script>\n```\n"
